        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 4. Cossura consimilis Read, 2000. Light microscopy. A–C (W.45625), compound microscope; D–H, stereomicroscope, stained with methylen blue.(A) thoracic region, dorsal view; (B) anterior part, dorsal view; (C) anterior part, lateral view; (D) W.45625, anterior part, dorso–lateral view; (E) W.45626, anterior fragment, lateral view; (F)W.45626, anterior end, lateral view; (G) W.45626, anterior part, dorsolateral view; (H) W.45625, posterior region, ventral view. Scale bars: A, D, E = 500 μm, B, C, F, H = 200 μm, G = 100 μm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4684833/files/figure.png" .

